column5: Hello,Does anyone have any info for the road going west to Wabeshkok lake and Catchalot lakes for access. We had built a bridge 2 years ago to get us out of that area as the road had washed out. I am wondering if they had rebuilt that road up again. Any info would be appreciated. Also was wondering if the ice is off of these lakes.Thanks for the comments.
Just bringing to top. Does anyone have any info on this. Thanks
